                      int thread_idle)
        Constructs a WeblogicServer using given parameters. This object provides a unique, immutable, Weblogic server set of metrics.
        Parameters:
        timestamp -
        servername - Name of the server registered in the Weblogic host
        server_state - State of the server registered in the Weblogic host
        health - Health of the server registered in the Weblogic host
        heap_free - Free Heap space of the server registered in the Weblogic host
        thread_idle - Number of idle threads in the server registered in the Weblogic host
